{"tid":1012953,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"吳彥祖IG用「醜豬」拜年 內地網民質疑辱華","createTime":"2019-02-08T03:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T04:15:18.000Z","uid":147522,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bc0cc29ea067fee9caeec78a6c34dee10e152b67","tid":1012953,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:44:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uW6agpr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuW6agpr.png&h=75b5c0ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一代男神吳彥祖在IG上向大家拜年，不過雖然是豬年，他卻貼出的不是可愛的豬照，而是一幅奇怪醜惡的豬。他又以廣東話拼音及英語祝福大家恭喜發財、新年快樂：「Happy Chinese New Year everyone！May the year of the pig bring you much health and happiness！！Gung Hei Fat Choy！Xin Nian Kuai Le！！！」<br />\n<br />\n而此「豬圖」換來內地網民不滿，批評豬長得太醜，質疑他辱華。不過亦有網民認為幽默一下而已，也有網民反批內地網民玻璃心。"},{"pid":"fea02ef6ff93ec5d877928d6524228c1e0aa4165","tid":1012953,"uid":50835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"支那人真係玻璃心到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1186e326c9028b854af65d42379149cd4ab08e91","tid":1012953,"uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fea02ef6ff93ec5d877928d6524228c1e0aa4165","tid":1012953,"uid":50835,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"支那人真係玻璃心到呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T03:56:06.000Z","msg":"Po隻豬都俾人鬧<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c20ac63bc9ade215f9913219cf5bd62ca022992","tid":1012953,"uid":58223,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:05:06.000Z","msg":"自己先入為主以為串緊自己 咁無人幫到你喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f5719ea07da2384809954a950a5586a07c486b","tid":1012953,"uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8c